headline: Future of Frozen Food 2025 Report Reveals New Frozen Food Trends and Generational Insights
summary: The rise in GLP-1 use, appetites for spice and heat, and indulgent in-home dining experiences, are just some of the trends driving growth identified in Conagra Brands' second annual Future of Frozen Food 2025 report. This data-driven report reveals how consumer behaviors, generational preferences, and innovations are reshaping the $91.3 billion U.S. frozen food market.1
